Key Match Events: WICKET: Edwards c Jaker Ali b Mustafizur 25 (Ned 116-5)
Post-Match Reflections: Tim Pringle loses his leg stump. It's been a horror ten balls for him against quality bowlers. I don't see Bangladesh as serious hot contenders and I think they will find that next level of competition tough.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Tigers are second in Group D on four points, two behind leaders South Africa. If they beat Nepal, they're through. The Dutch need to beat Sri Lanka and hope.
